productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Albertina has one of these. She works as a gardener and she says it looks humongous.
My co-worker Luka has one of these. He says it looks purple.
I tried to cremate it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
I saw one of these in Saint Lucia and I bought one.
My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
